54
00:03:07,716 --> 00:03:08,937
Oh, this is ridiculous.

55
00:03:10,815 --> 00:03:11,857
- What?
- Hello.

56
00:03:12,651 --> 00:03:16,028
I realize you're currently at the mercy
of your primitive biological urges,

57
