I don't know your sad song.

112
00:06:10,328 --> 00:06:12,566
I don't have a sad song.
I'm not a child.

113
00:06:15,223 --> 00:06:18,118
You know, I do understand
what you're going through.

114
00:06:18,243 --> 00:06:19,002
