115
00:06:19,373 --> 00:06:22,444
Did you just have the Nobel Prize
in waitressing stolen from you?

116
00:06:23,838 --> 00:06:27,271
Well, no, but when I was a senior
in high school,

117
00:06:27,396 --> 00:06:30,055
