is even remotely
comparable to a Nobel Prize?

125
00:06:48,665 --> 00:06:50,215
They're pretty tasty.

126
00:06:52,474 --> 00:06:55,492
And on a different,
but not unrelated topic,

127
00:06:55,617 --> 00:06:58,368
based on your current efforts
to buoy my spirits,

128
